ife, etc.?<br /><br /><br /><br />","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 year ago","ctime":"April 6 2016, 00:37:00 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"I have a whole new respect for editing","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://sourbillytipton.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"sourbillytipton","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"sourbillytipton","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://sourbillytipton.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"sourbillytipton","ctime_ts":1459903020,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/125136925/76218046","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24203696#t24203696","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24203696#t24203696","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24203696#t24203696","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"jaemi_z_h","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://jaemi-z-h.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24203696,"talkid":94545,"etime_ts":"1460331205","thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24203696#t24203696","upictitle":"Jaemi Zahra-Hall: pic#125136925","article":"Hi George, hope you are well. I just wanted to ask, did you write an open letter on dorkly . com?<br /><br />It purports to be a letter, by you, in defense of the frequent deaths in your work and how Shakespeare kills more of his characters and then how the Bible also features even more deaths.. I just wondered if it was genuine; and if it's not maybe you'd want to know cos it's not a small website. I don't like to be a tattle tail, but ou