speare, the style of the \"open letter\" is all wrong.<br /><br />Also, when I have something to say, I say it here.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 year ago","ctime":"April 11 2016, 05:47:36 UTC","parent":24203696,"massactions":0,"subject":"RE: Open Letter?","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"grrm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"grrm","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"grrm","ctime_ts":1460353656,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/125136925/76218046","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24204976#t24204976","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24204976#t24204976","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24204976#t24204976","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"jaemi_z_h","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://jaemi-z-h.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24204976,"talkid":94550,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/479920.html?thread=24204976#t24204976","above":24203952,"upictitle":"Jaemi Zahra-Hall: pic#125136925","article":"Right; thought so. I take your point about posting stuff here, nonetheless I thought it best to check. The piece does make some salient points, and it seems to come from a place of support, if not respect, since pretending to be you actually diminishes it.<br />Thanks for your response anyway. Jaemi x","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 year ago","ctime":"April 12 2016, 13:30:43 UTC","parent